# Common Workflow

```bash
pwd

ls -la

cd ~/linux-practice

mkdir project

cd project

touch README.md

cat > README.md

Linux Practice Project

Ctrl + D

cat README.md

head -n 5 README.md

tail -n 5 README.md

wc -l README.md

nl README.md

cp README.md README_backup.md

echo "Version 2" >> README_backup.md

diff README.md README_backup.md

tree
```

